<!-- S2: FFT -->
<section class="hidden" id="s2">
<div class="section-label">02 · FOURIER TRANSFORM</div>
<div class="section-title">FFT Visualizer</div>
<div class="section-sub">The Fast Fourier Transform decomposes a time-domain signal into its constituent frequency components. A 1024-point FFT reveals 512 frequency bins, each representing a narrow band of the audio spectrum from 0 Hz to the Nyquist frequency.</div>
