<div class="section-title">Spectral Freeze</div>
<div class="section-sub">Spectral freeze captures a frame of frequency-domain data and sustains it indefinitely. The result is a pitched, reverb-like drone — the spectral snapshot of a transient instant held outside of time. Pioneered by Max Mathews at Bell Labs.</div>
